  ('36fabd36-d622-80ce-cb9d-7b0a4e58fccb', 'ES', 'Spain', 'Other Dry-Cured Meats (Non-Iberian)', 'Embutidos Rodríguez', '', 'León, Castilla y León', 'L', TRUE, 'embutidosrodriguez.com', 'Spain''s largest cured-beef (cecina) producer. Cecina de León IGP is dry-cured, smoked beef hindquarter — a Spanish specialty. Strong supermarket distribution and growing premium-tier export. Mid-tier positioning, accessible.', 'L3', '["Cecina de León IGP"]'::jsonb),
