  ('ed032327-250c-c6d6-fee2-ec0372f3758b', 'ES', 'Spain', 'Olive Oil Houses', 'Almazaras de la Subbética (Cooperative)', '', 'Sierras Subbéticas Natural Park, Córdoba', 'L', TRUE, 'almazarasdelasubbetica.com', 'Founded 2007 from cooperative merger. Flagship oils: **Rincón de la Subbética** (monovarietal Hojiblanca), **Parqueoliva Serie Oro** (Picuda + Hojiblanca coupage). Multiple "World''s Best Mill" awards. Premium organic-and-sustainable positioning. Reference cooperative for Iriska volume sourcing.', 'L3', '["Priego de Córdoba DOP"]'::jsonb),
