  ('93b9015e-a3f3-ecf2-9271-ac27bd4180ed', 'ES', 'Spain', 'Conservas Gallegas (Galician Seafood — Mussels, Cockles, Razor Clams, Sardines, Octopus)', 'Conservas Hijos de Ramón Peña', '', 'Cambados, Galicia (Rías Baixas)', 'M', TRUE, 'ramonpena.com', 'Heritage producer (since 1920, third generation). 50+ products: cockles, clams, razor clams, mussels, small sardines, eel, cod and hake roe. ISO 9001 certified, "Pesca de Rías" seal. Premium positioning; reference brand for Galician Rías quality. Modern facility built 1998.', 'L3', '["Mejillón de Galicia DOP"]'::jsonb),
